ActIndian Act
Saskatchewan Treaty Land Entitlement Act
SubjectLittle Pine Indian Reserve No. 116, Saskatchewan ** Grant of Easement **
PrecisOrder (1) consenting to the exercise by TRANSGAS LIMITED of the power to take an interest in lands within LITTLE PINE INDIAN RESERVE NO. 116, Saskatchewan; and (2) granting the Company the required easement for natural gas transmission pipeline purposes.
